**Hari 2:** 4 curl chat queries return respons masuk akal
**Hari 3:** record_sale → stock berkurang → transaction di Atlas
**Hari 5:** Production URL health OK, response < 5 detik, 10 concurrent users

Prioritaskan task hari ini sebelum fitur nice-to-have.
